/** 
 * Sets the origin, which is used to calculate the distance from. This method should not be called while sorting. If done anyway, the contract of compare method will be broken and the sorting results are undefined, if by chance no Exception is thrown.
 * @param newOrigin the new location to calculate distances from.
 */
public void setOrigin(Vector3f newOrigin){
  origin.set(newOrigin);
}
